        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>URLs for hovered links in status bar could be immediately overwritten</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>'Search Messages...' dialog could not be opened outside the email tab</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Creating an event or task from mail failed if the mail was opened in a tab</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>NNTP message pane did not show network error page when network was lost</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Delete button could remove attachment instead of message</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>Folders sorted incorrectly when manually ordering them</p>
          
        </li>
      
    
      
        
        

        

        
        

        
        

        <li>
          <p>New folders were not added alphabetically if folders manually reordered beforehand</p>
          
